# DESCRIPTION
# Computation of expressions involving floor and
# ceiling functions
# WeBWorK problem written by Michael E. O'Sullivan
# and Thomas Schmidt
# ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Functions)
## DBsection(Piecewise functions)
## Institution(SDSU)
